article_title: SwedishAmerican opening new wellness center next month at YMCA

article_metadata.description: ROCKFORD - People can seek out services including weight management counseling and massage therapy next month at the new SwedishAmerican BetterLife Wellness center, a partnership with the YMCA of Rock River Valley.The center is located near the main entrance of the I.D. Pennock Family YMCA, 200 Y Blvd.SwedishAmerican is leasing the space and spent more than $300,000 renovating the area to include classrooms, space for massage therapy and yoga, and private counseling rooms for the members.
article_metadata.author: Melissa Westphal Rockford Register Star
